car rental system
                    SYSTEM ANALYSIS
The process of analysing the system that existed and alterations that are made in
the proposed system is stated in system analysis. a car rental system involves a 
comprehensive examination of the current processes and identifying areas for improvement to
develop a robust, efficient, and user-friendly system. This analysis aims to understand
the needs of the business, the end-users, and how technology can enhance operations. 
It starts with gathering requirements from stakeholders, including management, employees,
and customers, to ensure the system addresses all necessary functionalities 
such as vehicle management, customer management, rental transactions, and payments.
